er, heavy pill/badge density, and neon overload, utilizing the Apple-like GFF AI premium theme (using gradients from `#E4000F` to `#009DFF`).\n\n#### 4. Interaction Strategy\n- **Role Switching**: Hot-swapping user roles via the local developer switcher directly updates standard UI components, mimicking true Role-Based Access Control (RBAC).\n- **Simulated Delays**: Timeout promises in form submissions provide realistic network latency, reinforcing the premium, strategic feel of the live-action telemetry"}}
