y, and neon overload, utilizing the Apple-like GFF AI premium theme (using gradients from `#E4000F` to `#009DFF`).\n\n#### 4. Interaction Strategy\n- **Role Switching**: Hot-swapping user roles via the local developer switcher directly updates standard UI components, mimicking true Role-Based Access Control (RBAC).\n- **Simulated Delays**: Timeout promises in form submissions provide realistic network latency, reinforcing the premium, strategic feel of the live-action telemetry.\n- **Toast Notifications**: Used extensively to handle action confirmations, e.g., signature commitments, ledger exports, and simulated PDF invoice downloads.\n\n#### 5. Mobile Strategy\n- Sidebar-to-drawer transformations, responsive table-to-card reflows, and flex-wrap utility layouts are used to prevent horizontal scroll issues on mobile screens.\n\n#### 6. Files Aud"}}
